commit.message: Fixes player surfing on water and spamming warning prefabs
Changes to difficulty and event frequency
Adds two big platforms for usability, tutorial, and safety wall

Also changes the sorting layer in the player prefab

Improves usability

Player above all else, easier jumps
Fixes bugs, mainly a mis-sized hitbox
Fixed issues with Director and added difficulty scaling
